OL,3,CCumbrian mum backs campaign for
OL,4,Crestrictions on new drivers
OL,6,FA Cumbrian mum is campaigning for a
OL,7,Fchange in the law for newly passed
OL,8,Fdrivers, after her daughter was killed
OL,9,Fin a car crash.
OL,11,FCaitlin Huddleston was killed on the
OL,12,FA595 near Bootle in 2017 where she was
OL,13,Fa front seat passenger.
OL,15,FHer friend driving the car, who also
OL,16,Fdied in the crash, had passed her
OL,17,Fdriving test just four months earlier.
