OL,3,CCumbrian mum backs campaign for
OL,4,Crestrictions on new drivers
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Sharron
OL,7,FHuddleston, said: "We are hearing it
OL,8,Fweek after week now that cars full of
OL,9,Fteenagers are being killed.
OL,11,F"I know now that Caitlin would be
OL,12,Falive if we had certain elements of
OL,13,Fgraduated driving licences implemented
OL,14,Fin this country.
OL,16,F"That is where young drivers do not
OL,17,Fcarry their young or teenage friends
OL,18,Fas passengers for a limited time after
OL,19,Fpassing their test.
OL,26,@oD@SOU
