OL,3,CCumbrian mum backs campaign for
OL,4,Crestrictions on new drivers
OL,6,F"This allows them to gain experience
OL,7,Fdriving solo or with an older
OL,8,Fexperienced driver with them. We know
OL,9,Fthrough research that they are up to
OL,10,Ffour times more likely to crash when
OL,11,Fcarrying passengers.
OL,13,F"The positives for a graduated driving
OL,14,Flicence would be to reduce road
OL,15,Fcasualties and that would take the
OL,16,Fpressure off the NHS.
OL,18,F"If there are less young deaths on the
OL,19,Froad then insurance premiums would be
OL,20,Fa lot less as well.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
