OL,3,CCumbrian mum backs campaign for
OL,4,Crestrictions on new drivers
OL,6,F"A graduated driving licence would
OL,7,Freduce those deaths on the road. It is
OL,8,Fa positive law."
OL,10,FSharron added: "It is a lonely place,
OL,11,Fcampaigning.
OL,13,F"I have reached out to other families
OL,14,Fas well and we have set up a group
OL,15,Fcalled 'Forget Me Not Families
OL,16,FUniting' because we do feel forgotten
OL,17,Fabout.
OL,19,F"It devastates families, this can't go
OL,20,Fon any longer. Enough is enough with
OL,21,Fthese young deaths on our roads."
