OL,6,FEdmund King OBE, AA President said:
OL,7,F"The AA is launching our motoring
OL,8,Fmanifesto and one of the main points
OL,9,Fis around the safety of young drivers.
OL,11,F"20% of young drivers crash in their
OL,12,Ffirst year and up to 1500 are killed
OL,13,For seriously injured each year.
OL,15,F"What we are saying is for the first
OL,16,Fsix months or so we should limit the
OL,17,Fnumber of passengers young drivers
OL,18,Fhave so they can gain experience
OL,19,Frather than crashing early on and
OL,20,Fcosting lives.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
