OL,3,CCumbrian mum backs campaign for
OL,4,Crestrictions on new drivers
OL,6,F"One of the ways to police this would
OL,7,Fbe if we introduced a mandatory 'P'
OL,8,Fplate on the cars.
OL,10,F"Then the police and others would know
OL,11,Fif there were same age passengers in
OL,12,Fthe car then they would be able to
OL,13,Fstop that vehicle.
OL,15,F"What we find with young drivers is
OL,16,Fevery extra passenger that is in the
OL,17,Fcar, it increases the chances of
OL,18,Fcrashing by four times.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
